        <p>Strategic guidance for newsrooms, publishers, and startups on audience engagement, newsletter growth, product strategy, and revenue diversification.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="expertise-card">
        <span class="card-emoji emoji-hover" data-animation="pop">&#x1F91D;</span>
        <h3>Community Building</h3>
        <p>Designing programs and platforms that turn passive audiences into engaged, connected communities. From civic tech to local media to membership models.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

